            "summary": "In Montreal, Mandatory and NuORDER by Lightspeed, top B2B commerce platforms are collaborating once again to support Mandatory's in-person trade event in Copenhagen from August 5-7. This partnership, now in its third year, highlights the growing trend of hybrid commerce, blending physical and digital interactions for enhanced buying experiences. This initiative aligns with the Nordic fashion industry's growth, showcasing the intersection of physical and digital commerce for increased flexibility and innovation.",
